          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">The </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Selected-Segment</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> has been removed from the motion.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">There is one less segment in the motion.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Notes:</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">The </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Segment Width</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> of the </text><text styleclass="Interface" translate="true">Previous-Segment</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> increases by the </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Segment-Width</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> of the segment that you delete.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">You will not get a warning that you will delete the segment. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">Do </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">CTRL+Z</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> to undo, but the </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Motion-Width</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> may increase.</text></para>
